                            <comment id="41546" author="morrone" created="Thu, 5 Jul 2012 20:21:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Oh, and remove all of the commented-out includes as well.  Thats bad to leave them in the manual.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="41545" author="morrone" created="Thu, 5 Jul 2012 20:20:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looks like lustre_idl.h is needed in at least some of the examples.  liblustre.h still needs to be removed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
